366
00:28:58,770 --> 00:29:00,302
Baik.

367
00:29:03,520 --> 00:29:04,738
Terima kasih, Pak.

368
00:29:04,762 --> 00:29:05,928
Bagus.

369
00:29:06,678 --> 00:29:07,930
Coleman, Howe.

370
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:10,350
Kalian akan dapat penugasan baru pekan ini.

